@startuml deep-fm-class-structure
title DeepFM 模型类层次结构
caption PyTorch 实现的核心组件及其关系

skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor #333333
    FontSize 11
}

class "FeaturesEmbedding" as Embedding #LightBlue {
    - field_dims: List[int]
    - embed_dim: int
    - embedding: nn.ModuleList
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 为每个稀疏特征\n生成嵌入向量
}

class "FMFirstOrder" as FMFirst #LightGreen {
    - field_dims: List[int]
    - linear: nn.Linear
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 线性部分
}

class "FMSecondOrder" as FMSecond #LightGreen {
    - field_dims: List[int]
    - embed_dim: int
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 特征交叉
}

class "FactorizationMachine" as FM #LightGreen {
    - first_order: FMFirstOrder
    - second_order: FMSecondOrder
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
}

class "MultiLayerPerceptron" as MLP #LightCoral {
    - layers: nn.ModuleList
    - dropout: float
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 深度神经网络
}

class "DeepComponent" as Deep #LightCoral {
    - embedding: FeaturesEmbedding
    - mlp: MultiLayerPerceptron
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
}

class "DeepFMModel" as DeepFM #LightYellow {
    - embedding: FeaturesEmbedding
    - fm: FactorizationMachine
    - deep: MultiLayerPerceptron
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 组合 FM 和 Deep
}

class "CTRModel" as CTRModel #LightYellow {
    - deepfm: DeepFMModel
    + forward(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    + predict(X: Tensor) -> Tensor
    note: 输出 CTR 概率
}

Embedding <|-- FM
Embedding <|-- Deep

FMFirst <|-- FM
FMSecond <|-- FM

MLP <|-- Deep

FM +-- DeepFM
Deep +-- DeepFM

DeepFM <|-- CTRModel

note right of Embedding
  <b>嵌入层 (共享)</b>
  - 为每个类别特征
    生成稠密向量
  - 参数高效
end note

note right of FM
  <b>FM 组件</b>
  - 一阶: 线性部分
  - 二阶: 特征交叉
  - 低阶交互
end note

note right of Deep
  <b>Deep 组件</b>
  - MLP 多层感知机
  - 高阶非线性
  - 复杂模式
end note

note bottom of DeepFM
  <b>关键设计</b>
  1. 嵌入层共享
  2. FM + Deep 并行
  3. 端到端训练
  4. 低高阶组合
end note

@enduml
